<DATELINE> FORT WORTH, Texas  </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Stevens Graphics Corp. said it acquired Bernal Rotary Systems Inc. of Troy, Mich. 
Terms weren't disclosed. 

   Bernal makes rotary cutters and creasers used in packaging printing materials and has annual revenue of more than $15 million. 
Stevens makes offset-printing presses, collators and packaging equipment. 

